            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_43wh' title='Col. 43WH &mdash; HC Deb 20 April 2004 vol 420 c43WH' name='column_43wh' href='#column_43wh' rel='bookmark'>43WH</a>
            mathematics of the enterprise. Should we not be looking for improved numeracy and mathematical skills at high levels of government?
          </p>
